# Minimal test: lattice with basis
units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p
lattice custom 3.998 a1 1.0 0.0 0.0 a2 0.0 1.0 0.0 a3 0.0 0.0 4.187
basis 0.0 0.0 0.0
basis 0.5 0.0 0.5
basis 0.0 0.5 0.5
basis 0.5 0.5 0.0
region r1 block 0 2 0 2 0 2 units lattice
create_box 1 r1
create_atoms 1 box
variable N equal count(all)
print "N = ${N}"
